      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still has plenty of heart? I\u2019m parting with my trusty car, and it has been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it the perfect companion for your daily commutes or fun weekend getaways. It runs beautifully and is totally ready for its next adventure with you! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
