      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies. This unit is mated to a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory M-Variable differential lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS unit refresh and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. The chassis dynamics are preserved via upgraded bushings and a tuned suspension setup that provides excellent turn-in response. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the powertrain remains robust, delivering linear torque and a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. An ideal specimen for the purist seeking a balance of analog performance and mechanical longevity.",
